1. *Đavo* je izvadio mač iz pojasa. (The devil pulled out a sword from his belt.)
2. U đavolovoj kući proživela je tisuću noći. (She lived a thousand nights in the devil's house.)
3. Rekli su da *đavo* ne štedi nikoga. (They said that the devil spares no one.)
4. U daljini se čuo đavolov smijeh. (The devil's laughter was heard in the distance.)
5. Strah od *đavola* često uzdrma srca ljudi. (Fear of the devil often shakes the hearts of people.)